      "file_path": "cps-ri/src/main/resources/changelog/changelog-master.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "NB: I think a db tag will hardly ever be changed. Since the CPS team changes db schema/model(like tables, indexes, etc.) rarely.\n\nThus no suffix/prefix is needed. However, we can accommodate a versioning once (as suggested in the link above I shared) by starting it with a value like version_1.0\n\nAlso, we can ask E/// about their version format.",
